data.description: Come and make this remodeled 3 bedroom/1 bath ranch home in Golfview Highlands your next home. Decorated in today's colors including fresh paint, new carpeting and newer LVP flooring. Kitchen features white shaker cabinets and counter top space for meal prep. You will appreciate the fact the roof is newer on the home and garage as well as the vinyl siding, the windows in the home, the electrical service, HVAC, the water heater and plumbing are all newer. WOW!!! You can just move right in and enjoy the things that are most important to you. Over sized 2.5 car garage will accommodate all your vehicles, tools and toys with ease. The asphalt driveway is 2 cars wide to accommodate 8-10 vehicles. There is even a graveled side drive area along the garage for your boat or sleds!!! Don't miss this home that is available immediately!!!
